        4       0       0       CD always On    &C0
                16      10      CD tracks presence of data carrier (see also
                                S38b3) &C1
        5       0       0       CTS follows RTS, in synchronous mode    &R0
                32      20      Ignore RTS (CTS always On), in synchronous mode         &R1
        6-7     0       0       Ignore DTR signal, assume DTR always On         &D0
                64      40      108.1, DTR Off-On transition causes dial of the
